Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.10,0:00:09.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サクラ)二人とも… 笑ってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:13.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,あぁ。 その絵を 描いたとき➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:16.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,初めて ホントに笑ってた。 心から…。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.79,0:00:19.79,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)こ… これは…！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:28.84,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)サイのバッグの中に あった…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:33.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)これは 暗部の者が\N己のターゲットを記す 暗殺リスト…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:35.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)いわば ビンゴブックだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:38.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,暗殺リスト…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:44.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,この ×印… 何なんです？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:49.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,これは おそらく ターゲットを\Nすでに 抹殺したという印だろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.63,0:02:52.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,でも…\Nなんで そんなものを サイが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.79,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)見ろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:02:59.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サクラ)これって…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:03.14,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケ…!? なんで サイが…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:07.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サイ)忍法 超獣偽画！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:11.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,まだ ×印が ついていない…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:16.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,そうか…\Nそういうことだったのか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:18.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,どういうことだってばよ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:21.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)サイ… アイツの任務は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:26.45,japanese,,0,0,0,,大蛇丸とダンゾウとの パイプ役に\Nなることなんかじゃ なかった…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:41.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,サイの本当の… 極秘任務は…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケの 暗殺だったんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:10.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,そんなこと…\Nあるわけねえってばよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:14.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,だって さっき アイツは\Nサスケを 助けるって…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:18.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,それに！\Nホントに… 心から 笑ってた…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:21.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,((サイ : 兄さんに 見せたかった…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.95,0:04:25.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,(二人の夢の 絵を…))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:28.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,今までと違って アイツは もう…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:31.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,それが 全部…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:34.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルトを 出し抜くための➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:37.14,japanese,,0,0,0,,芝居だったとしたら…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:39.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,((ボクは ダンゾウ様の手足だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:42.14,japanese,,0,0,0,,ボクは 存在しない。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:45.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,だから ボクに 何を言っても…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:47.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,(無意味なんだよ…))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:58.14,japanese,,0,0,0,,この ビンゴブックの持ち主なら\Nやりかねないよ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:05:00.14,japanese,,0,0,0,,これを 見ろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:06.98,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)サスケの隣に載っている\Nこの男…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:09.62,japanese,,0,0,0,,霧隠れの上忍で 木ノ葉に対し➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:12.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,強硬姿勢を示していた男だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:16.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,サイが… 倒したんですね？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:20.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,うん…。 簡単に 倒せる相手じゃ\Nなかったはずだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:22.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)それを\N抹殺したということは…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:27.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,おそらく\Nありとあらゆる手段を講じたはず。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:31.79,japanese,,0,0,0,,他人を 出し抜くための芝居などは\N日常茶飯事だったろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:36.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,笑顔は 目的を達するために…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:39.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,((サイ : 騙されたな～。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:42.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,キミの さっきの 作り笑い…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:45.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,しかし 作り笑いにも➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:47.64,japanese,,0,0,0,,そんな使い方が あるんだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:50.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,覚えておくよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:54.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,…オメエは\N殴られて なに ヘラヘラしてんだ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:59.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,厄介事を やり過ごすには\N笑顔が いちばん。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:06.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サイ)それが 作り笑いでもね…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:10.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,意外と みんな 騙される。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:13.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サイ)そう 本に書いてあった))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:16.62,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)この\Nビンゴブックに 記されている人物を➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:19.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,一人ひとり見れば よく わかる。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:21.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,サイは 木ノ葉に対する➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,危険人物の処理に\Nあたっていたんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:27.48,japanese,,0,0,0,,そして サスケも…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:30.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,その 危険人物の一人…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:47.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)ダンゾウの目的は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:49.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,大蛇丸の 新たなる肉体…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケを 葬ることだった…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:57.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,そのために サイは\N大蛇丸に 近づこうとしたんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:00.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)木ノ葉を\N裏切ったわけでは なかった…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:03.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)ただ 木ノ葉のためにと…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:09.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,武闘派の 考えそうなことだ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:19.65,japanese,,0,0,0,,ここで ゴチャゴチャ話してても\Nしようがねえってばよ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:22.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,サイが どんな命令を受けたとか➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.34,japanese,,0,0,0,,ダンゾウってヤツが\N何を 考えてるかなんて➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:27.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,どうでもいい！\N一刻も早く サイと合流して➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:32.64,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケを見つけ出すことが 重要だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:37.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,確かに ナルトの言うとおりだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:39.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,さっき サイのチャクラを感じた。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:42.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,急いで 向かうよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:44.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,あぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:46.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,わかったってばよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:56.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,《サクラ : サイが…\Nサスケ君を 狙ってるのだとしたら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:59.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,私が… 絶対に 止めてみせる！》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サスケ)誰だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:13.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,バレちゃいましたか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:17.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,でも…\Nボクは もう 先手をとっている…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:22.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,目的は なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:25.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,ダンゾウ様の 目的は…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:27.85,japanese,,0,0,0,,キミを 葬ること。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:33.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,ボクは… キミを…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:37.79,japanese,,0,0,0,,《サイ…！》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:42.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉へ 連れ帰る！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:53.32,japanese,,0,0,0,,最も 最初は キミを殺すつもりで\N来たんだけど…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:59.62,japanese,,0,0,0,,((アイツは… 誰よりも オレのことを\N認めてくれた 一人だ！))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:05.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,((ナルトは… サスケ君のことを➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:07.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,(兄弟みたいに 思ってるから…))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:11.48,japanese,,0,0,0,,((その仲間を 救うためなら…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:13.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんだって やるさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.81,0:09:17.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,(お前とだって… 組んでやる！))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:20.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,((たとえ バラバラに されようが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:23.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは 大蛇丸から…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:26.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サスケを\N奪い返してやるんだってばよ！))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:31.48,japanese,,0,0,0,,((サスケは… オレの友達だ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:35.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,(やっと できた…\N大切な つながりだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:39.64,japanese,,0,0,0,,ボクは… 彼が 必死に\Nたぐり寄せようとしている➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:42.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,キミとの つながりってのを…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:44.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,守ってみたいんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:53.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,つながり…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:04.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,そんなことのために\Nオレの眠りを ジャマしたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.06,0:10:22.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんだ…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:28.55,japanese,,0,0,0,,サイの チャクラだ。\Nあっちのほうね！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:37.88,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんだ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:40.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,《カブト : サスケ君か…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:44.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,寝起きは 機嫌が悪いからね…\Nあの子は…》
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:15.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,うっ… さすがですね。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:20.45,japanese,,0,0,0,,ボクの術を強引に振りほどくとは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,《見つけた！》
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:38.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,サクラ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:49.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,アンタ ホントは 何が狙いなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:51.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,私たちを何回 裏切れば…！\Nサクラか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:59.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,《この声…》
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:32.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケ君…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:57.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:18.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルトか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:24.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前までいたのか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:33.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,なら カカシもいるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:38.68,japanese,,0,0,0,,カカシさんでなくて残念だけど\Nボクが代理だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:42.68,japanese,,0,0,0,,これから カカシ班は\Nキミを 木ノ葉に連れ帰る。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:50.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,カカシ班か…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:05.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,サイ！ あなた やっぱり！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:13.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソイツが オレの穴埋めか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:22.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,また ぬるいヤツが入ったもんだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.26,0:16:27.56,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルトと オレのつながりを\N守りたいだのなんだの言ってたが。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:34.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,サイ あなたの任務は サスケ君を…。\N(サイ)確かに ボクの極秘任務は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:36.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケ君の暗殺だった。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:39.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,けど 命令は もういい。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:42.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,今は 自分の考えで動きたい。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:46.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト君が\N思い出させてくれそうなんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:49.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,ボクの昔の気持を…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:53.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,何か とても\N大切だった気がするものなんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:16:58.91,japanese,,0,0,0,,ボクは キミのことを\Nよく知らないけど➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:03.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト君やサクラさんが ここまで\N必死に キミを追うのには➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:05.75,japanese,,0,0,0,,何か訳がある。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:08.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,キミとの つながりを切るまいと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:13.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,つなぎ止めておこうと\N必死になっている。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:16.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,ボクには まだ\Nはっきりとはわからない。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:21.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,けど サスケ君…\Nキミには わかっているはずだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:26.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,ああ… わかっていた。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:34.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,だから 断ち切った！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:55.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,((ふざけんな～っ!!))
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:18.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,((上等だ～っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:20.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,うっ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:24.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,《なんで…》
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:32.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,《あのときから\N少しも縮まらない…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:34.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,この差は なんだ？》
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:48.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,(イタチ)お前は 弱い。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:53.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,なぜ弱いか…\N足りないからだ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:55.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,憎しみが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:13.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,(うわぁぁぁぁっ!!))
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:19.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレには 別のつながりがある…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:20:03.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,兄との憎しみっていう\Nつながりがな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:15.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,今日のテーマは ナルトをめぐる\N「つながり」についてよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:19.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サクラ)生い立ちゆえに\N誰にも認められず➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:23.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,孤独だったナルトを\N初めて認めてくれた人…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:25.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,それは イルカ先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:29.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルトが 初めて手にした\N大切な つながりね。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.11,0:21:32.91,japanese,,0,0,0,,そして 仲間という つながりを\N作るきっかけとなる➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.91,0:21:35.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,私たち カカシ班が結成された。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:39.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,その後のナルトは 持ち前の\N負けん気と がんばりで➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:41.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,里のみんなにも認められ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:44.98,japanese,,0,0,0,,次々と つながりの輪を\N広げていったのよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:49.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,人と人とを結ぶ つながりの糸は\N時を経るに従い➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:52.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,太く 力強くなっていく。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:54.75,japanese,,0,0,0,,一度\Nこの糸を持ってしまった人間は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:58.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,相手のことを理屈抜きで\N放ってはおけない。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:02.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,イルカ先生の言葉だけど\N心に残る言葉よね。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:04.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,みんなも 自分の\Nつながりの糸を➡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.93,0:22:06.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,探してみてね。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.93,0:00:09.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both smiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:14.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... He smiled for real for\Nthe first time when he drew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.40,0:00:16.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiled from the bottom of his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:19.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.87,0:01:52.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reunion\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:27.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It was in Sai's bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:31.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an assassination list\Nthat has...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.57,0:02:33.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,an Anbu Black Ops member's\Nown targets recorded...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:35.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called a Bingo Book.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:37.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,An assassination list...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:44.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these "X" marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,In all likelihood,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:49.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,they're marks indicating targets\Nthat have already been eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:52.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Sai have such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:56.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:02:59.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.13,0:03:02.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke...\NWhy does Sai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:06.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Art: Super Beast Scroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:09.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no "X" mark on this yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:15.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it...\NSo that's what this is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:18.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:19.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:25.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,His mission wasn't to be a go-between\Nfor Orochimaru and Danzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:40.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sai's true classified mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:55.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,was to assassinate Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:10.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That could never be!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:14.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he said earlier that\Nhe was going to save Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:18.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And he really smiled from\Nthe bottom of his heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:21.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is what I wanted\N{\i1} to show him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:24.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The picture of our dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:28.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike before, he's now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:29.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What if that was all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:35.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,an act in order\Nto forestall you, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:41.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm a tool for Lord Danzo.\N{\i1}I don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:46.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So no matter what you say to me,\N{\i1}it's pointless...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:54.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The owner of this Bingo Book...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:57.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,could indeed be capable\Nof something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:04:59.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:05.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This man in the book\Nnext to Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Jonin from\Nthe Hidden Mist...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:11.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and the man who expressed\Na hard-line stance against the Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:15.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sai...defeated him, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:19.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't have been\Nan easy opponent to defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:22.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that he eliminated him\Nmeans that in all likelihood,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:25.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,he must have resorted\Nto every possible means.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:29.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,An act in order\Nto forestall someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:30.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,was probably all in\Na day's work for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:35.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,A smile is used\Nto carry out a goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:41.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You tricked me with\N{\i1}your fake smile earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:47.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that's how you use\N{\i1}a fake smile, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:50.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:54.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can you grin like that\N{\i1}after getting punched?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:58.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A smile is the best way\N{\i1}to get through a tough situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:03.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if it's a fake smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:08.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Surprisingly enough,\N{\i1}everyone gets fooled...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It said that in a book...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:17.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite clear by looking\Nat each of the people listed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:18.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,in this Bingo Book...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:23.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sai was assigned to the disposal\Nof people dangerous to the Leaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:29.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And Sasuke is also\None such dangerous person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Danzo's goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:51.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,was to bury Orochimaru's new flesh...\Nto bury Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:54.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:56.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sai attempted\Nto approach Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:07:02.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't betray the Leaf.\NIt was for the sake of the Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:09.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what one from\Na hard-line military faction would think up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:17.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in going on\Nabout that here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:22.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter\Nwhat Sai was ordered to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:25.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,or what that Danzo guy's\Nthinking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:28.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting up with Sai\Nas quickly as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:31.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and saving Sasuke\Nis what's important!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:36.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's indeed as Naruto says.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:41.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt Sai's Chakra earlier.\NWe need to go quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:46.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Sai is after Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:59.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then I'll stop him,\N{\i1}no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:08.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:12.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You found me out, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:17.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But...I've already made\Nthe first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:20.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:27.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Danzo's objective is\Nto bury you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:33.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:37.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:41.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,...take you back to the Leaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:49.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Although at the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:52.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here with the intention\Nof killing you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:58.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's the person who acknowledged me\N{\i1}more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:07.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Naruto...thinks of Sasuke\N{\i1}like a brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:13.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll do whatever it takes\N{\i1}to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:17.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll even team up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I get chopped up\N{\i1}into pieces,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:25.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll take Sasuke back\N{\i1}from Orochimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:30.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sasuke is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:34.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a special bond\N{\i1}I was finally able to make...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:39.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect\Nhis bond with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:43.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,the one he's desperately trying to\Ndraw closer to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:52.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Bond...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:03.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You interrupted my sleep\Nfor something like that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:21.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sai's Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:28.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:36.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:39.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sasuke, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.27,0:10:43.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That kid wakes up in\N{\i1}a bad mood, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:20.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,To think he'd break free\Nfrom my Jutsu by force...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:35.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:37.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:49.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You!\NWhat're you really after?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do you have\Nto betray us until you're satisfied...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:51.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:12:58.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:31.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sa...su...ke...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:56.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:17.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:24.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,So even you were here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:32.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Then is Kakashi also with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:37.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it's not Kakashi...\NI'm his substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:42.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Team Kakashi will now be taking you\Nback to the Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:50.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Team Kakashi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:05.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sai! I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.73,0:16:13.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's my replacement, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:20.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Some soft one has once again\Njoined up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:24.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he wanted to protect\Nthe bond...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:26.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,between Naruto and me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:32.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sai... I thought your mission\Nwas to kill Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:36.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,My classified mission was indeed\Nthe assassination of Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:39.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,